        quotes.add(new Quote("Harry Potter","“Slowly, very slowly, he sat up, and as he did so he felt more alive, and more aware of his own living body than ever before. Why had he never appreciated what a miracle he was, brain and nerve and bounding heart? It would all be gone...or at least, he would be gone from it. His breath came slow and deep, and his mouth and throat were completely dry, but so were his eyes.”"));
        quotes.add(new Quote("Harry Potter","“I don't think you should be an Auror, Harry,\" said Luna unexpectedly. Everybody looked at her. \"The Aurors are part of the Rotfang Conspiracy, I thought everyone knew that. They're working to bring down the Ministry of Magic from within using a mixture of dark magic and gum disease.”"));
